{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"75143ead-431e-44c4-8c84-e7ac7b6abc86","content":"I found the following issues with `.template.config/template.json`:\n\n1. **Missing `identity` field** (required) — Every template must have a unique `identity` string that identifies the template to the engine.\n\n2. **Invalid `datatype` value** — `\"invalid-type\"` on line 9 is not a recognized datatype. Valid values are: `bool`, `choice`, `float`, `int` (or `integer`), `hex`, `text` (or `string`).\n\n**Example fix:**\n```json\n{\n  \"author\": \"Test\",\n  \"classifications\": [\"Test\"],\n  \"identity\": \"Test.Template\",\n  \"name\": \"Test Template\",\n  \"shortName\": \"build\",\n  \"symbols\": {\n    \"myParam\": {\n      \"type\": \"parameter\",\n      \"datatype\": \"string\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0dc82d8c-552a-41f0-ae84-2226ecfb5392","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Let me analyze this template.json file. This is a .NET template configuration file (used by `dotnet new`). Let me check for issues:\n\n1. **`author`**: \"Test\" - valid string, OK\n2. **`classifications`**: [\"Test\"] - valid array of strings, OK\n3. **`name`**: \"Test Template\" - valid string, OK\n4. **`shortName`**: \"build\" - valid string, OK (though \"build\" is a reserved name in some contexts, it's technically valid)\n5. **`symbols`**: Object with one parameter definition\n   - **`myParam`**: \n     - `type`: \"parameter\" - valid\n     - `datatype`: \"invalid-type\" - This is NOT a valid datatype. The only recognized datatypes are `bool`, `choice`, `float`, `int`/`integer`, `hex`, and `text`/`string`.\n\nThere's also a missing `identity` field, though it's technically optional depending on the template engine version.\n\nSo I'm seeing two main issues: the `datatype` value is invalid, and the `identity` field is either missing or needs to be verified against the schema requirements.","outputTokens":678,"requestId":"1C1F:551B:AEA7202:BD4A2AC:69FD3380"},"id":"729a9b93-51f8-4e59-a7a1-bba0e737feeb","timestamp":"2026-05-08T00:51:27.370Z","parentId":"7f41346b-a0a2-439c-908b-f3c60a76b2e4"}
